'''富士X-Pro2'''是2016年1月发布的[[无反光镜可换镜头相机|无反光镜可换镜头数码相机]]。<ref name=annoucement>{{cite web | url = http://www.fujifilm.com/news/n160115_01.html | publisher = [[Fujifilm|Fujifilm]] | title = Taking performance to new heights,the 富士X-Pro2 offers the world's only Hybrid Multi Viewfinder and features a brand new 24MP X-Trans III sensor | date = 2016-01-15 | accessdate = 2016-01-16 | archive-date = 2020-11-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201124012122/https://www.fujifilm.com/news/n160115_01.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.engadget.com/2016/01/14/fujifilm-x-pro2/ | first = Edgar | last = Alvarez | publisher = [[Engadget|Engadget]] | title = 富士X-Pro2: The upgraded premium camera finally arrives | date = 2016-01-14 | accessdate = 2016-01-16 | archive-date = 2016-01-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160117222901/http://www.engadget.com/2016/01/14/fujifilm-x-pro2/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.dpreview.com/reviews/retro-through-and-through-fujifilm-x-pro2-first-impressions-review | publisher = [[DPReview|DPReview]] | title = Retro through-and-through: 富士X-Pro2 First Impressions Review | first1 = Richard | last1 = Butler | first2 = Samuel | last2 = Spencer | date = 2016-01-15 | accessdate = 2016-01-16 | archive-date = 2016-03-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160314003734/http://www.dpreview.com/reviews/retro-through-and-through-fujifilm-x-pro2-first-impressions-review | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.theverge.com/2016/1/14/10766824/fuji-x-pro-2-announced-specs-price-release-date | publisher = [[Vox_Media|Vox Media]] | work = [[The_Verge|The Verge]] | title = Fujifilm's X-Pro2 is finally here | first = Sam | last = Byford | date = 2016-01-14 | accessdate = 2016-01-16 | archive-date = 2016-01-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160118011158/http://www.theverge.com/2016/1/14/10766824/fuji-x-pro-2-announced-specs-price-release-date | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://gizmodo.com/fujifilm-x-pro2-fujis-top-mirrorless-shooter-returns-w-1753104046 | publisher = [[Gizmodo|Gizmodo]] | title = 富士X-Pro2: Fuji's Top Mirrorless Shooter Returns With Fury | first = Mario | last = Aguilar | date = 2016-01-14 | accessdate = 2016-01-16 | archive-date = 2016-01-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160117201251/http://gizmodo.com/fujifilm-x-pro2-fujis-top-mirrorless-shooter-returns-w-1753104046 | dead-url = no }}</ref>2015年10月末有记者发现富士在中国大陆[[工信部|工信部]]注册了一款名叫“X-Pro2”的无线局域网设备<ref>{{Cite web|title=富士X-Pro 2将在近期发布|url=http://dcdv.zol.com.cn/546/5469696.html|accessdate=|author=|date=2015-10-21|format=|publisher=中关村在线|language=}}</ref>，两个月之后富士就推出了X-Pro2。X-Pro2是[[富士|富士]][[富士X系列|X系列]]相机的一部分，是[[富士X-Pro1|X-Pro1]]的后继产品，其下一代产品是[[富士X-Pro3|X-Pro3]]。X-Pro2于2016年3月3日开始发售。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fujifilm.co.jp/corporate/news/articleffnr_1035.html?_ga=1.77900951.2022930864.1452614480 |title=新開発のセンサーとプロセッサーにより、「Xシリーズ」史上最高の画質と機動性を実現　プレミアムミラーレスカメラ「富士X-Pro2」 |accessdate=2020-12-02 |archive-date=2016-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021014412/http://www.fujifilm.co.jp/corporate/news/articleffnr_1035.html?_ga=1.77900951.2022930864.1452614480 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

X-Pro2是第一款具有双SD卡插槽的无反光镜可换镜头相机。 富士对X-Pro1的布局进行了一些更改，并加了一个操纵杆。

X-Pro2与其他参评的产品共同获得了2016年日本相机大奖赛（Camera Grand Prix Japan 2016）编辑奖。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cjpc.jp/gra/2016/grandprix16E.html |title=Camera Grand Prix 2016 |accessdate=2020-12-02 |archive-date=2020-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813114547/http://www.cjpc.jp/gra/2016/grandprix16E.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==重要特征==
* 2430万像素，[[APS-C|APS-C]]画幅[[富士X-Trans传感器|X-Trans CMOS III]] [[图像传感器|传感器]]
* 与[[富士X卡口|富士X卡口]]镜头系统兼容
* [[感光度|ISO]] 200–12800，可扩展至ISO 100–51200
*支持[[1080p|1080p]]60帧或[[4K分辨率|4k]]30帧的视频录制（4k需要升级固件到4.0及以上版本）<ref>"[http://www.fujifilm.com/support/digital_cameras/software/firmware/x/xpro2/history.html Firmware update history(up to version 4.00)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fujifilm.com/support/digital_cameras/software/firmware/x/xpro2/history.html |date=20191017010105 }}". [[Fujigilm|Fujigilm]]. Accessed 2 April 2018.</ref><ref>"[http://www.fujifilm.com/news/n170907_06.html Updated:New firmware updates for FUJIFILM X-Pro2, X-T2 X100F, X-T20 coming soon.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fujifilm.com/news/n170907_06.html |date=20201109033635 }}". [[Fujifilm|Fujifilm]], 7 September 2017. Accessed 2 April 2018.</ref><ref>Michael Zhang, "[https://petapixel.com/2017/09/07/fujifilm-firmware-updates-coming-x-series-x-pro2-get-4k-video/ Fujifilm Firmware Updates Coming for X Series: X-Pro2 to Get 4K Video] {{Wayback|url=https://petapixel.com/2017/09/07/fujifilm-firmware-updates-coming-x-series-x-pro2-get-4k-video/ |date=20200314174239 }}". [[PetaPixel|PetaPixel]], 7 September 2017. Accessed 2 April 2018.</ref>
*混合[[OLED|OLED]] /光学[[取景器|取景器]]
* 1/8000秒机械[[快门|快门]]
*双存储卡插槽（首次用于无反光镜可换镜头相机）

